title: 11/17/2020 - HOUR 1 - Harden, Vikings, empowerment

description:
James Harden is not a number 1

Teams like the Vikings need a better QB and are in quicksand

James Harden, Kevin Durant, and Kyrie Irving on the same team could be a disaster

Player empowerment is great for the player but it might be hurting the league


Guest: Peter King
